1
00:00:05,000 --> 00:00:07,440
Ijkuak in tlajtlamach* yonochiu,

2
00:00:07,440 --> 00:00:12,580
Jesús oyaj Jerusalén kampa on hebreos* kichiuayaj sen iluitl para Dios.

3
00:00:12,580 --> 00:00:14,720
Ipan on ueyikalpan,

4
00:00:14,720 --> 00:00:18,280
nisiu itech on tsakuijlotl* itoka de las Ovejas,

5
00:00:18,280 --> 00:00:24,200
onkatka kampa naltilo yejuan ikan tlajtojli hebreo* itoka Betesda.

6
00:00:24,200 --> 00:00:28,360
Ne kampa naltilo kipiyaya makuijli kalmatsitsimej.

7
00:00:28,360 --> 00:00:34,720
Niman ompa ipan on kalmatsitsimej tejtemiyaj miyekej kokoxkej yejuan koxomej,

8
00:00:34,720 --> 00:00:37,680
ciegos niman on yejuan sepouiyaj.

9
00:00:37,680 --> 00:00:40,640
Yejuamej kichixtikatkaj ma nolini on atl,

10
00:00:40,640 --> 00:00:48,840
pampa san ajsiya on tiempo ijkuak sen ángel temouaya ne ijtik kampa naltilo niman koxoniaya on atl.

11
00:00:48,840 --> 00:00:56,200
Kemaj on yejuan achtopa kalakiya ijtik on atl pajtiya maski san katlejua kualolistli kipiyaya.

12
00:00:56,200 --> 00:01:02,160
Ompa nemiya sen tlakatl yejuan ye kipiyaya treinta y ocho xipan ika kualouaya.

13
00:01:02,160 --> 00:01:04,960
Ijkuak Jesús okitak ompa onok,

14
00:01:04,960 --> 00:01:07,560
niman okitak ika ye uejkaui kualo,

15
00:01:07,560 --> 00:01:08,840
okitlajtoltij:

16
00:01:08,840 --> 00:01:10,600
—¿Tikneki tipajtis?

17
00:01:10,600 --> 00:01:12,840
On kokoxki okijlij:

18
00:01:12,840 --> 00:01:14,560
—Señor,

19
00:01:14,560 --> 00:01:19,560
xnikpiya akinon nechkalaktis ijtik on atl ijkuak nolinia.

20
00:01:19,560 --> 00:01:23,000
Ijkuak nikneki nikalakis,

21
00:01:23,000 --> 00:01:25,640
okse achtopa kalaki.

22
00:01:25,640 --> 00:01:26,880
Jesús okijlij:

23
00:01:26,880 --> 00:01:28,320
—Xmotelketsa.

24
00:01:28,320 --> 00:01:31,000
Xkajkokui mopetl niman xuiya.

25
00:01:31,000 --> 00:01:33,040
Nimantsin on tlakatl opajtik,

26
00:01:33,040 --> 00:01:35,800
okontilan ipetl niman onejnen.

27
00:01:35,800 --> 00:01:41,200
Pero in onochiu ipan on tonajli ijkuak noseuiyaj on hebreos*.

28
00:01:41,200 --> 00:01:46,600
Yejua ika intlayekankauan on hebreos* okijlijkej on yejuan opajtik:

29
00:01:46,600 --> 00:01:49,240
—Aman in tonajli sábado.

30
00:01:49,240 --> 00:01:53,360
Itlanauatil Moisés xmitskauilia para tikmomamaltis mopetl.

31
00:01:53,360 --> 00:01:55,400
On tlakatl okinmijlij:

32
00:01:55,400 --> 00:01:58,600
—On yejuan onechpajtij onechijlij:

33
00:01:58,600 --> 00:02:02,000
“Xkajkokui mopetl niman xuiya.”

34
00:02:02,000 --> 00:02:03,800
Kemaj okitlajtoltijkej:

35
00:02:03,800 --> 00:02:05,680
—¿Akinon omitsijlij:

36
00:02:05,680 --> 00:02:08,040
“Xkajkokui mopetl niman xuiya”?

37
00:02:08,040 --> 00:02:11,760
Pero on tlakatl xkimatiya akinon okipajtij,

38
00:02:11,760 --> 00:02:17,640
pampa Jesús onejkuanij itech on miyek tlakatl yejuan ompa nemiya.

39
00:02:17,640 --> 00:02:22,480
Más sakin* Jesús okinextij ne ipan on ueyitiopan,

40
00:02:22,480 --> 00:02:23,520
niman okijlij:

41
00:02:23,520 --> 00:02:24,720
—Xkaki,

42
00:02:24,720 --> 00:02:26,640
aman yotipajtik.

43
00:02:26,640 --> 00:02:32,440
Maka oksejpa titlajtlakos para maka mopan nochiuas itlaj yejuan más temojtij.

44
00:02:32,440 --> 00:02:40,680
Kemaj on tlakatl oyaj niman okinmachistito intlayekankauan on hebreos* ika on yejuan okipajtij yejua Jesús.

